@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### FR-01: katalog produk
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### FR-02/FR-03/UC-03: pelanggan membuat pesanan, estimasi stok tetap dicatat walau kurang
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Role: pelanggan

{
  "customer_name": "Pak Yusuf",
  "customer_contact": "08129990000",
  "order_type": "bulk",
  "needed_at": "2026-07-26",
  "note": "Untuk acara keluarga",
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
      "quantity": 20
    }
  ]
}

### FR-04: admin melihat daftar pesanan
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
X-Role: admin

### FR-05/BR-07: admin konfirmasi dulu
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Role: admin

{
  "status": "dikonfirmasi"
}

### FR-08/FR-12/UC-11: pindah ke diproses memvalidasi dan mengurangi stok otomatis
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Role: admin

{
  "status": "diproses"
}

### FR-10/FR-11: restock manual
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stock/adjustments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Role: admin

{
  "ingredient_id": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "kind": "masuk",
  "quantity": "1000",
  "note": "Restock tepung dari supplier lokal"
}

### FR-13/FR-16: stok kritis
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stock/critical
X-Role: admin

### FR-14: riwayat pergerakan stok
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stock/movements
X-Role: admin

